text: trying to go out to a bunch of delicious meals in the next month before baby. what awesome places have you eaten at recently?
we've been to Masu and Irving St Kitchen in the last week, good quality as always but nothing new/surprising. The Pearl district is the James Beard of LakeO restaurant chains
Bollywood theater is a must. City State diner on NE 28th for brunch is divine. And of course, Miss Delta for a damn good southern meal
Just had brunch at Tin Shed with my housemates and it was INSANE. Their biscuits are so good and I had such a hard time picking between all of their amazing brunch items
masu has a great happy hr
this was great and fun, tho i would prob skip the kimchee cocktail next time:  <http://hanoakpdx.com/>
the main courses were amazing.  not too crazy expen$ive too
